<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686631>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Abyssorchomene abyssorum (Stebbing, 1888), ♀, 9.5 mm (ZMH K-61206); ♂, 7.0 mm (ZMH K-61207), DIVA-3 M79/1 station 531, Southwest Atlantic, Argentine Basin, depth 4586 m., 15 July 2009. Female eye position/size shown is approximate. Outer ramus is oriented on the left side of the uropods. Figures with sex not indicated are of female. Scale bars = 0.1 mm unless indicated otherwise." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686631/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686635>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Abyssorchomene abyssorum (Stebbing, 1888), ♀, 9.5 mm (ZMH K-61206). Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686635/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686639>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Abyssorchomene abyssorum (Stebbing, 1888), holotype, ♂, 7.5 mm (BMNH 1889.5.15.23). Scale bar = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686639/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686641>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Abyssorchomene abyssorum (Stebbing, 1888), holotype, ♂, 7.5 mm (BMNH 1889.5.15.23). Setae omitted on Mxpd. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686641/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686633>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Abyssorchomene abyssorum (Stebbing, 1888), ♀, 9.5 mm (ZMH K-61206). Rows of pectinate setae omitted on propodus of Gn2 detail. Scale bars = 0.5 mm unless indicated otherwise." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686633/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686645>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Abyssorchomene abyssorum (Stebbing, 1888), holotype, ♂, 7.5 mm (BMNH 1889.5.15.23). Gills missing from P3–7. Outer ramus is oriented on the left side of the uropods. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686645/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686637>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Abyssorchomene abyssorum (Stebbing, 1888), holotype, ♂, 7.5 mm (BMNH 1889.5.15.23). Most aesthetascs omitted from A1 callynophore. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686637/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686643>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Abyssorchomene abyssorum (Stebbing, 1888), holotype, ♂, 7.5 mm (BMNH 1889.5.15.23). Setae omitted on merus-propodus outline of Gn2. Scale bars = 1 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686643/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686663>
    dc:description "Fig. 17. Abyssorchomene patriciae sp. nov., holotype, ♀, 10.5 mm (NHM UK 2022.6); allotype, ♂, 7.5 mm (NHM UK 2022.7). Figures with sex not indicated are of female. Scale bars = 0.5 mm unless indicated otherwise." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686663/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686687>
    dc:description "Fig. 25. Abyssorchomene scotianensis (Andres, 1983), ♀, 12 mm (CMNC 2022-0005); ♂, 12.4 mm (CMNC 2022-0007). Outer ramus is oriented on the left side of the uropods. Figures with sex not indicated are of female. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686687/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6686707>
    dc:description "Fig. 33. Abyssorchomene shannonae sp. nov., holotype, ♀, 12 mm (ZMH K-61209); allotype, ♂, 7 mm (ZMH K-61210). Outer ramus is oriented on the left side of the uropods. Figures with sex not indicated are of female. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6686707/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

